British Airways Reviews Analysis Dashboard
Project Overview
This project is an interactive Tableau dashboard built to analyze customer reviews and passenger experience data for British Airways flights. The dashboard consolidates review metrics, customer feedback, traveler demographics, and service ratings to identify trends in customer satisfaction and operational performance.
The project demonstrates practical data analytics skills including:
•	Data cleaning and transformation
•	Exploratory data analysis (EDA)
•	Dashboard development in Tableau
•	KPI analysis and visualization
•	Customer sentiment and service performance analysis
•	Geographic and trend-based reporting
________________________________________
Objective
The primary goal of this project is to:
•	Analyze customer review patterns across different flight and traveler categories
•	Evaluate airline service quality metrics
•	Identify strengths and weaknesses in passenger experience
•	Provide actionable business recommendations based on customer feedback
•	Build an interactive business intelligence dashboard for decision-making
