Dataset Overview
The dashboard uses airline review data combined with country-level geographic information.
Main Dataset: ba_reviews.csv
Contains customer reviews and airline service ratings.
Data Structure
Column Name	Description	Data Type
Author	Review author/customer	String
Date	Review submission date	Date
Place	Customer location	String
Content	Customer review text	String
Aircraft	Aircraft model used	String
Traveller Type	Type of traveler (Business, Family, Solo, etc.)	String
Seat Type	Cabin class (Economy, Business, First Class, etc.)	String
Route	Flight route	String
Date Flown	Flight travel date	Date
Recommended	Whether the customer recommends the airline	String
Trip Verified	Whether the review was verified	String
Rating	Overall customer rating	Integer
Seat Comfort	Seat comfort score	Integer
Cabin Staff Service	Cabin crew service rating	Integer
Food Beverages	Food and beverage rating	Integer
Ground Service	Airport/ground support rating	Integer
Entertainment	In-flight entertainment rating	Integer
Value For Money	Customer value perception rating	Integer
