Key Insights
Customer Experience Insights
•	Cabin staff service and seat comfort strongly influence overall ratings.
•	Value for money ratings often vary significantly across traveler types.
•	Some aircraft models consistently receive higher customer satisfaction scores.
•	Verified reviews provide more reliable indicators of operational performance.
Operational Insights
•	Customer sentiment changes across different months and travel periods.
•	Geographic analysis highlights regions with stronger or weaker customer perception.
•	Premium seat categories generally show higher satisfaction metrics.
